This product composes the agent-governance-plane (AGP) governance runtime,
licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0:
  https://github.com/jeremylongshore/agent-governance-plane

AGP provides the policy gate, Docker sandbox, Slack human-in-the-loop approval,
and the signed, hash-chained audit journal. Bob the Intendant adds the
trigger-woken watcher agent, the watch operator surface, agent templates, and
the installer.
